trong>Selen</strong> Tatsuki的合同。对此，海外对ANYCOLOR进行了激烈的批评，有可能出现取消NIJISANJI EN（新）艺人订阅数的动向。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="avk9TJdYpd"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/">ANYCOLOR公司NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Selen Tatsuki的合同被取消</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR 取消了 NIJISANJI EN（新）所属 VTuber Selen Tatsuki 的合同” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/embed/#?secret=UMxWQusnlB#?secret=avk9TJdYpd" data-secret="avk9TJdYpd" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>此外，据称是Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声优模特的VTuber <strong>Dokibird</strong>的订阅人数自2月5日起迅速增加，截至2月7日22:00，订阅人数约为309,000人。已经完成。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="jYerzWImE4"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-selen-tatsuki-supposed-actor-dokibird-expressed-her-gratitude-youtube-subscribers-exceeded-300k/">VTuber Seren Ryugetsu表演者/声优“Dokibird”致谢频道订阅人数达30万</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声优“Dokibird”表达了他的谢意，订阅人数已达到30万” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-selen-tatsuki-supposed-actor-dokibird-expressed-her-gratitude-youtube-subscribers-exceeded-300k/embed/#?secret=0aKAv3Mx3R#?secret=jYerzWImE4" data-secret="jYerzWImE4" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div cla