</style><p>2月5日，运营《NIJISANJI EN》的公司ANYCOLOR<em>对据称曾担任Dokibird表演者/声优模特的Seren Ryugetsu发出投诉，并宣布将因其行为而终止合同</em>。对此，ANYCOLOR在海外受到了批评，但似乎有很多人支持Dokibird并订阅了该艺术家的官方YouTube频道。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="VQ8ZNXpxg8"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/">VTuber Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声音模型“Dokibird”订阅人数迅速增加</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“据说是 VTuber Seren Ryugetsu 的表演者/声音模特的“Dokibird”频道的订阅人数迅速增加” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/embed/#?secret=8SR7R5jXP7#?secret=VQ8ZNXpxg8" data-secret="VQ8ZNXpxg8" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="LA1p1IS00V"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/">ANYCOLOR公司NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Selen Tatsuki的合同被取消</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR 取消了 NIJISANJI EN（新）所属 VTuber Selen Tatsuki 的合同” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/embed/#?secret=fSdFAZIA4L#?secret=LA1p1IS00V" data-secret="LA1p1IS00V" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://youtube.com/@Dokibird" target="_blank" rel="noreferr